Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.02,0:00:08.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,300)}{\c&HA0A0A0&}This story is fiction. The names of people,\Nplaces and groups are imaginary.\NObey traffic rules and drive safely.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.75,MainStyle,,0100,0000,0310,,{\bord0}INITIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Information, spreads in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:32.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we don't know how to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who say, "Money can't buy my love..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.34,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...deserves a lariat three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.27,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We make love according to the manuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.24,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't notice the lack of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we suffocate, let's yell. Ho!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:44.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midnight dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:47.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,No place to relax in the sleepless city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:51.91,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We smile without dropping our guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:56.02,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to lie and the truth is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.07,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I desperately wanna shut and break out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:01.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we gotta start.  Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.69,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move into the brand new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.95,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dive into the brand new trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:09.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of a big world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.97,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.94,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we go full speed and funky beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.57,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.52,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.42,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho! Here we go to an unknown world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.42,0:01:22.17,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a newborn traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.22,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable footsteps are fun to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:26.32,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Get things done right, only when needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.84,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:30.14,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes, you'll receive slanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.18,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's warp uninteresting things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.67,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,..and lead at least a rational life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:35.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonuva...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit my car from\Nbehind, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:52.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.\NIt was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:56.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so slow, I couldn't\Npredict your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:02:00.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to enter\Nthe corner so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:04.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't brake in time,\Nand I touched your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:05.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Iketani!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:12.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to apologize,\Nwe'll race by our rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and if you win, I'll kneel\Ndown to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By your rules?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:24.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it a gumtape death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gumtape death match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:32.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there's a fast Eight-Six\Ndownhill driver in the Speedstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:39.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the Eight-Six brat that I'll be waiting\Nhere at 10:00pm next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:03:01.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?\NHe challenged Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:04.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't know Takumi's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:08.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, take his challenge, whether\Nit's a gumtape death match or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat the guy, and make\Nhim kneel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid, it's\Ntoo risky, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't be able to steer\Nduring the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:20.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Iketani, Takumi has defeated\Nthe FD and 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't lose just because\Nof some customized rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, that guy must've practiced\Na lot under that rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:31.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, don't race at such\Na disadvantage, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any intention of racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's good.\NJust ignore him.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.60,0:03:49.10,MainStyle,,0000,0070,0127,,{\fad(970,1000)}{\2a&HFF&}Itsuki's First Date
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NA gumtape death match?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:10.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.\NAnd what about Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's calm and uninterested like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't feel like racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Takumi to race!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:27.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll outrun that jerk, make him\Nkneel down, and we'll feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's driving a Civic, the archrival\Nof Levins and Truenos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:39.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when we were young,\Nwe used gears and rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the gumtape death match was\None of the most dangerous battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is a gumtape death match\Nreally that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:53.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, get in your car\Nand give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:04.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, steer full to either left or right, while keeping\Nyour right hand on the steering wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,O...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn any farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:15.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave the steering wheel as it is\Nand get out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:16.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Now see how far you steered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:19.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,O...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:26.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It only turned that much?!\NI thought I steered a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you turn in the corners?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't drive in the mountain passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only use steering\Nto initiate the turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:39.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You must slide the rear tires\Nto clear the corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:46.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But Takumi's good at drifting,\Nso he'll be able to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:53.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't countersteer, which\Nmakes drift control difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:56.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he oversteers a bit,\Nhe'll go into a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:06:00.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he understeers at the entrance,\Nit'll be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:04.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This rule gives FF cars an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent is an EG6, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:12.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the EG6 has an FF layout, he can cope\Nwith oversteering using the gas pedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:16.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he can also minimize the "under"\Nby using the parking brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for an FR like the\NEight-Six to race safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like a circus tightrope walker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...he has to drift throughout the race\Nand maintain extreme control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd better not do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:34.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, if he heard that,\Nhe might become interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:48.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, it's about that jerk\Nfrom the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I did a little investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Shoji Shingo of the Myogi Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoji Shingo of the Night Kids...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's supposed to be their number two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:03.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he claims to be the fastest\Nof the Night Kids on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But he doesn't choose normal means\Nto accomplish his goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so the other members\Ndon't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:13.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He especially doesn't get along with\Ntheir leader, Nakazato Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:13.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:19.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wants to defeat Takumi\Nto gain influence in the Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going around spreading\Na nasty rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  A rumor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:25.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:29.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Speedstars are scared, and\Nwe won't accept his challenge."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't say anything about it\Nbeing a gumtape death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're the only ones who'll look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:41.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to drag Takumi into\Nracing him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,M...me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Means nothing to me.\NI won't accept his challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:57.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you've been challenged,\Nit's too ridiculous to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,O...okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about the battle\Nwith the Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's their move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:18.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drag that Eight-Six brat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be an interesting battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:28.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingo, you seem to be planning something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...just don't disgrace the name\Nof the Night Kids, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:39.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the one who's disgraced\Nour name already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the one who was totally outrun\Nby a brat in a dated Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a high powered 32, at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A loser should go bark somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:02.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you preaching to me\Nas if you'll be our leader forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:06.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato, I'll avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You should thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:20.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Shingo, you'll eventually see\Nhow great the Eight-Six is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:28.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, Takeshi is on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:30.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, he was so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, the leader of the\NNight Kids is you, Shingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:42.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, I'll send Akina's\NEight-Six to the junkyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:02.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Takeuchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Saori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Itsuki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go driving to Akina Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting at the bus stop at 1:00pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My 18 years of life without\Na girlfriend is finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:54.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is a gumtape death match...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.\NNever mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Gumtape death match, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:34.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}You're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:37.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...good at driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:46.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}If it's with you....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}...I don't mind staying overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:53.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I think of her a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:21.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:24.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He was washing a car a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:32.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're neglecting work\Nin a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:39.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I'm just taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:42.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual to see you reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Love manual?\NHow to romance a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:51.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:56.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Reading a book like this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've got a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,With that babe, Saori,\Nyou talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you get ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:10.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought the book on the way home yesterday,\Nand I've been studying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:14.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to things like this,\NI don't think I can depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:18.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're straightforward.  It can't\Nbe helped because it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are so convenient these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to find out everything\Nby ourselves in my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:31.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's an established fact, to get close\Nto a girl by the third date..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:35.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"...create a romantic mood\Nfor the first kiss..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly prepared, Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:42.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm taking a day off,\Nlike I told you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it's all about.\NI guess it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm envious of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Saori...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your answer about\Nthe gumtape death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You told the Eight-Six guy\Nabout it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no intention of racing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:10.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina's Eight-Six driver is a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:14.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The gumtape death match\Nscared him off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything to make him race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:53.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We Road Racers don't say, "turn into the curve,"\Nwe say, "tackle the corner."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get a license.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:00.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you?\NI'll teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:11.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina Fuji...\NIt's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:19.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}"Girls react to the mood.\NDo the first kiss in a romantic setting."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}First kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's the right chance!\NGo for it, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:51.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:35.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The mood is heavy.\NI'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:01.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}An EG6...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He tapped my bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Does it mean I should\Nget out of the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:17.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's right on my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:21.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Shit, I have to be decisive\Nin front of Saori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori, I'm gonna speed up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:27.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bear with it for a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:42.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle between Road Racers...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}At...at least Saori...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:46.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:48.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki had an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:49.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:52.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,On Akina's mountain pass!\NHe was taken to the city hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You two go check on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:55.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as bad as it looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:14.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they're keeping me\Nhere to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:17.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Saori?\NShe was with you, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:20.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She only got a scratch,\Nso she went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:23.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I steered hard so I wouldn't\Ncrush the passenger side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:26.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...your Eight-Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:31.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It spun just right, so it only suffered\Nminor damage to the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.24,0:21:33.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:34.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:47.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going downhill on Akina,\Nand an EG6 tailgated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,An EG6?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, because it was a red EG6.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was suddenly bumped\Nfrom behind in a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:01.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That asshole did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:02.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:04.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's a gumtape death\Nmatch or not, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:09.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:14.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,S...sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be taken in by his strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A gumtape death match is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:23.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.19,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,My pride says "You gotta be wild and tough."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:52.20,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't let others meddle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.06,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Never stop. I don't want to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:55.99,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I sacrifice my crying lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:58.33,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Head for the peak, and sweep the winding street.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.23,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep, beep! The warning sounds so cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:01.68,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The sheep should make room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.68,0:23:03.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,`Cos I'm never gonna stop streakin' my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:06.02,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Your motivation is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.02,0:23:07.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is simulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:11.94,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you want to break out,\Nyou'll end up in a safety zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:15.88,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You obtain something while\Nyou lose something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:19.88,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't change, even if the world is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:27.93,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Beasty shout. No one can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:35.33,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The raging dream goes beyond time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:39.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Rage your dream to break through the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.35,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a stream to the peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:47.33,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It will eliminate the frozen night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:51.39,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Rage your dream to explore the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:54.33,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Di-ding dang, another round, never slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:56.12,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock down in comma zero one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.37,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You head for the next town, leaving trails.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:00.43,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Dust rises and the loser falls down to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:01.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The puffery, full of logic...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:04.04,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...is bothering, so let's ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:05.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The streaker disappears into the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:07.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Something they would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:08.33,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Rage your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:11.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the never-ending street...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:15.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...without looking back at your love or your past...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:19.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...you keep on going, so you shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.38,0:24:20.38,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Rage your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.38,0:24:24.30,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You live in the present.
