Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.30,0:24:32.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}You've caused Itsuki to have an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.62,0:24:35.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}You're playing dirty, aren't you, Shingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.14,0:24:38.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, as long as\NAkina's Eight-Six shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.31,0:24:39.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.25,0:24:44.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know my chances of winning the\Ngumtape death match are 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:48.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be fun to simply defeat him,\Nso I'll arrange an interesting show.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.86,0:24:53.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}N...next time on Initial D:\N"Improving Genius of Drift!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.89,0:24:58.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him experience\Ntrue fear in the downhill.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:25:00.03,MainStyle,,0000,0140,0407,,Initial
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:25:00.03,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:25:00.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0190,,Improving Genius of Drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:24:59.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Don't miss it!
